headline: T-Satellite is Here: And Now It’s Powering Apps!
summary: BELLEVUE, Wash., October 01, 2025--T-Mobile (NASDAQ: TMUS) today announced a major expansion of T-Satellite with Starlink, bringing satellite data connectivity for popular apps to dozens more smartphones. Essential tools like app-based voice and video chat, mapping, weather and social media sharing, among others, are now part of the T-Satellite experience.
